ielder's battle skill or ultimate applies Arts Susceptibility, the target enemy suffers Arts DMG Taken +10.8% for 20 s. The two effects apply separately and do not stack with themselves.","Detonate: Brigand's Bane (6/9) Cryo DMG Taken: +32% Cryo DMG Dealt +32% . When the wielder applies Cryo Infliction via battle skills or ultimates, the wielder gains Cryo DMG Dealt +40% for 20 s. When the wielder's battle skill or ultimate applies Arts Susceptibility, the target enemy suffers Arts DMG Taken +12% for 20 s. The two effects apply separately and do not stack with themselves.","Detonate: Brigand's Bane (7/9) Cryo DMG Taken: +35.2% Cryo DMG Dealt +35.2% . When the wielder applies Cryo Infliction via battle skills or ultimates, the wielder gains Cryo DMG Dealt +44% for 20 s. When the wielder's battle skill or ultimate applies Arts Susceptibility, the target enemy suffers Arts DMG Taken +13.2% for 20 s. The two effects apply separately and do not stack with themselves.","Detonate: Brigand's Bane (8/9) Cryo DMG Taken: +38.4% Cryo DMG Dealt +38.4% . When the wielder applies Cryo Infliction via battle skills or ultimates, the wielder gains Cryo DMG Dealt +48% for 20 s. When the wielder's battle skill or ultimate applies Arts Susceptibility, the target enemy suffers Arts DMG Taken +14.4% for 20 s. The two effects apply separately and do not stack with themselves.","Detonate: Brigand's Bane (9/9) Cryo DMG Taken: +44.8% Cryo DMG Dealt +44.8% . When the wielder applies Cryo Infliction via battle skills or ultimates, the wielder gains Cryo DMG Dealt +56% for 20 s. When the wielder's battle skill or ultimate applies Arts Susceptibility, the target enemy suffers Arts DMG Taken +16.8% for 20 s. The two effects apply separately and do not stack with themselves."]$essence$::jsonb, ARRAY[1, 2, 2, 3, 3]::smallint[], ARRAY[1, 1, 2, 2, 3]::smallint[], 6, 6, 4, 'https://www.icy-veins.com/arknights-endfield/weapons/brigands-calling', 'Published rank 1-9 values and skill descriptions; checked 2026-06-05', true, now())
on conflict (weapon_key) do update set
    primary_label = excluded.primary_label,
    primary_values = excluded.primary_values,
    primary_is_percent = excluded.primary_is_percent,
    secondary_label = excluded.secondary_label,
    secondary_values = excluded.secondary_values,
    secondary_is_percent = excluded.secondary_is_percent,
    skill_name = excluded.skill_name,
    skill_descriptions = excluded.skill_descriptions,
    primary_base_ranks = excluded.primary_base_ranks,
    secondary_base_ranks = excluded.secondary_base_ranks,
    primary_max_essence = excluded.primary_max_essence,
    secondary_max_essence = excluded.secondary_max_essence,
    skill_max_essence = excluded.skill_max_essence,
    source_url = excluded.source_url,
    source_note = excluded.source_note,
    verified = excluded.verified,
    updated_at = now();

update public.weapons as weapon
set
    main_attribute = profile.primary_label,
    secondary_attribute = profile.secondary_label,
    passive_name = profile.skill_name,
    updated_at = now()
from public.weapon_essence_profiles as profile
where weapon.weapon_key = profile.weapon_key
  and profile.verified = true;

commit;

select weapon_key, primary_label, secondary_label, skill_name, verified, source_url
from public.weapon_essence_profiles
order by weapon_key;
